messages.msgSnippet: #1 easiest video to understand is Live at Hollyw. Bowl.  H. Grail is a absurdly gross.  Life of Brian a bit sacrilegious (sp?), and Meaning of Life I saw in
messages.messageBody:
#1 easiest video to understand is "Live at Hollyw. Bowl." H. Grail is a absurdly gross. Life of Brian a bit sacrilegious (sp?), and Meaning of Life I saw in a theatre with 8 other people. 2 left. I sat with 2 others and laffed til I cried. Just me. By myself - the others were too floored!

Oh, and Now for Something Completely Different is not very funny (to me)

Oh, Oh, get DVDs or look on the tape box for captioning. You can miss tonnes with the wicked accents.

So ease into it with "Live at Hollyw. Bowl."unless you have an off-the-wall humour fanatic.

My (Pithon Monty) thots

Tim T
